{"tid":164553,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[求教]去英國 法國預算","createTime":"2017-03-20T17:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T15:25:57.000Z","uid":53297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ec56c10e170d46a39ea9de2bf308101bb6f26c","tid":164553,"uid":53297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:43:55.000Z","msg":"去12-14日 帶7萬左右 食普通野 會去唔同景點 大概每日最少用幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b654f470fb0568d06822767b110366337cad06a","tid":164553,"uid":53297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9eeb9345ac5350851a8db93206685f00dae0db1","tid":164553,"uid":48012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:48:04.000Z","msg":"睇你住咩 HKD150-500不等 (Hostel - Budget Hotel)<br />\n食HKD30-70一餐 (Meal deal - Pub)<br />\n車錢HKD25左右一程 (Tube/Tram)<br />\n<br />\n當所有野都最平 一日咪大概HKD300蚊<br />\n你自己再計埋去第二個城市d交通呀 等閒shopping呀 睇波呀個d錢囉<br />\n<br />\n法國唔知"},{"pid":"df2299730d6603723028ea7eb1f0f4c6ea24b39b","tid":164553,"uid":53297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:51:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你住咩 HKD150-500不等 (Hostel - Budget Hotel)<br />\n食HKD30-70一餐 (Meal deal - Pub)<br />\n車錢HKD25左右一程 (Tube/Tram)<br />\n<br />\n當所有野都最平 一日咪大概HKD300蚊<br />\n你自己再計埋去第二個城市d交通呀 等閒shopping呀 睇波呀個d錢囉<br />\n<br />\n法國唔知</blockquote><br />\n7萬唔包機票 酒店<br />\n5月尾去都收季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原本預每日大概食500 咁多日搭車5000 <br />\n其他shopping <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008658e5d750d5bf70319ed5310ffae951523d43","tid":164553,"uid":53297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:54:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1743d2f14d97b65cae4cb34c934c89ba17856656","tid":164553,"uid":43918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T18:24:55.000Z","msg":"洗費除左交通<br />\n<br />\n個人認為英國啲錢好用啲<br />\n因為你有唔少平既野食選擇<br />\n例如周街tesco/sainsbury's都有&pound;2-4既意粉薄餅呀中式飯揀下<br />\n如果要慳錢哩個係唔錯選擇<br />\n<br />\n反之法國唔興便利店<br />\n下下要出去食 &euro;10-20普通一餐<br />\n樓主可以諗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbd777114c1623d48623a5ceae29ace7e0f2d35","tid":164553,"uid":43918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T18:26:38.000Z","msg":"加多句<br />\n而家英鎊好平 買名牌會係全歐洲最平<br />\n試下官網禁哂英國/法國黎格價就知我講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過點都平過係on9 hk 買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee97779e97a7b914cdbee02f7f9c0ccc8dcc1f9","tid":164553,"uid":53297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:47:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗費除左交通<br />\n<br />\n個人認為英國啲錢好用啲<br />\n因為你有唔少平既野食選擇<br />\n例如周街tesco/sainsbury's都有&pound;2-4既意粉薄餅呀中式飯揀下<br />\n如果要慳錢哩個係唔錯選擇<br />\n<br />\n反之法國唔興便利店<br />\n下下要出去食 &euro;10-20普通一餐<br />\n樓主可以諗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法國可能去幾日 買野去返英國 好似平少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9564b943f1a55d71ba72301587d5e6a09beac6b2","tid":164553,"uid":53297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:48:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加多句<br />\n而家英鎊好平 買名牌會係全歐洲最平<br />\n試下官網禁哂英國/法國黎格價就知我講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過點都平過係on9 hk 買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBurberry係咪特別平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外想問Chanel LV 法國定英國平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c156018acef0cf21732d679af6b210d33538fe0","tid":164553,"uid":53297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:49:12.000Z","msg":"各位指教下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8081f3f414b0f41edbbf2321580e6a10ede54b52","tid":164553,"uid":43918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:23:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>加多句<br />\n而家英鎊好平 買名牌會係全歐洲最平<br />\n試下官網禁哂英國/法國黎格價就知我講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過點都平過係on9 hk 買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBurberry係咪特別平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外想問Chanel LV 法國定英國平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBurberry 你想買咩呀 頸巾機場免稅又無人爭係最平<br />\n但門市&pound;350有免費繡名<br />\n(Staff態度西到殺左佢全家咁)<br />\n<br />\nChanel/LV果啲我覺得英國無咁齊款同好多中東西施同你爭<br />\n但如果係大路款不防試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a198327fbc979e5a833f0dcc70d346256fa0aeae","tid":164553,"uid":53297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:57:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>加多句<br />\n而家英鎊好平 買名牌會係全歐洲最平<br />\n試下官網禁哂英國/法國黎格價就知我講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過點都平過係on9 hk 買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBurberry係咪特別平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外想問Chanel LV 法國定英國平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBurberry 你想買咩呀 頸巾機場免稅又無人爭係最平<br />\n但門市&pound;350有免費繡名<br />\n(Staff態度西到殺左佢全家咁)<br />\n<br />\nChanel/LV果啲我覺得英國無咁齊款同好多中東西施同你爭<br />\n但如果係大路款不防試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想買個普通LV銀包同Burberry外套送比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32b2fe36526f2568fd0442e00084682435a77da","tid":164553,"uid":53297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:58:41.000Z","msg":"同埋喺英國去埋法國要幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9e49d79bc0c06c90bc6e19eb5c78e37f4743ee","tid":164553,"uid":1025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T06:11:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你住咩 HKD150-500不等 (Hostel - Budget Hotel)<br />\n食HKD30-70一餐 (Meal deal - Pub)<br />\n車錢HKD25左右一程 (Tube/Tram)<br />\n<br />\n當所有野都最平 一日咪大概HKD300蚊<br />\n你自己再計埋去第二個城市d交通呀 等閒shopping呀 睇波呀個d錢囉<br />\n<br />\n法國唔知</blockquote><br />\n一餐pub food邊有咁平<br />\n唔飲野淨嗌一個fish and chip都最少7磅<br />\n淨係London 搭underground 唔貴但去第二個city 就最少平幾 london去Manchester/Leeds/York 就300幾走唔甩<br />\n<br />\n法國食飯仲貴<br />\n搭車要小心啲因為有時職員會突然檢查你嘅飛<br />\n之後話你張飛唔得 罰你三舊幾水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb84e60b8ab8e84ac1e146292a26e1a63c2a35d","tid":164553,"uid":1025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T06:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋喺英國去埋法國要幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nEurostar &pound;70一程<br />\nEasyjet /ryanair  &pound;50-60早買仲平"},{"pid":"bd1720a5a6d2f648e7d72f3ef8c672370c62e778","tid":164553,"uid":77104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T06:17:12.000Z","msg":"豪每日1k港紙都夠"},{"pid":"7938d3a46c81f7d177271d3603f1e4ebda26c204","tid":164553,"uid":53297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T06:58:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>豪每日1k港紙都夠</blockquote><br />\n咁都要買下野 手信㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496c67b3ac9c7216a29b603ef0aab3c36b0cb381","tid":164553,"uid":53297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}